gov.anl.ipns.ViewTools.Layouts
Interface IComponentLayoutManager

All Superinterfaces:
IPreserveState
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractLayoutManager, SingleLayoutManager
public interface IComponentLayoutManager
extends IPreserveState

This class defines methods needed for all LayoutManagers. Implementing classes will create a display from an IVirtualArray in a variety of views. Individual views are generated by classes implementing IComponentSwapper which make use of IViewComponents. LayoutManagers are a collection of individual views grouped together into a logical display. LayoutManagers will not be responsible for laying out ViewMenuItems or shared controls, that will be the job of the ComponentViewManager.
